# Project Overview

This is the personal website and blog of Ryota Murakami (laststance.io), built with Next.js 15 and the App Router pattern. The site includes:

- Personal blog with MDX-based articles
- Project showcase
- About page
- Uses page (tools/setup)
- Keybinds reference

## Key Project Principles

- Modern React patterns with App Router
- Server-first approach with React Server Components
- TypeScript for type safety
- Tailwind for styling
- Accessibility best practices
- Performance optimization
- Mobile-first design

## Development Guidelines

- Use pnpm for package management
- English only for code comments and documentation
- Follow proper TypeScript typing
- Prefer server components when possible
- Keep bundle size minimal

